data.description: Located in the highly desired Avery Park community this beautiful two story house has 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and two living rooms.  The layout of the house connects the living room, dining room & kitchen creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings. Nice looking kitchen with granite counter tops & back splash. Tile flooring throughout the first floor and carpet upstairs; nice large backyard with sprinklers system. This house is conveniently located near schools and shopping centers, community pool, sidewalks throughout and a soccer field area. Home is priced well because it comes with solar panels-allowing savings on electricity bills, it also has water softeners.
